name: Frog, Frogger, Froggest
description:
Made for Mini Jam 79: Frogs

Theme: Frogs

Limitation: One Level

Its inspired by Frogger but its horizontal...and endless.

!!! Playing on Mobile is possible but very bad !!!

You are a frog and need to dodge all the cars. The Objective is to see how high your High Score is.

Controls: Arrow Keys
